{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wizard Shrimp\u2122 is a bullet-hell, roguelite game where you play as a Shrimp who is inexplicably also a Wizard?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle your way out of a slimy swamp, escape amethyst caves, before climbing the Mushroom Wizard's Tower to defeat the final boss.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect upgrades and power ups along your quest to become the most powerful Shrimp this world has ever seen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gain Krill points to power up your Shrimp and take on the game at harder difficulties in the Cauldron!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pixel art graphics are accompanied by a modern soundtrack that mixes digital and analogue sounds, embracing naturalistic samples.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your own path out of each area with a unique randomly generated tile system. Leverage your tiles to your tactical advantage by putting a campfire after an enemy encounter. Or say &quot;f*** it&quot; and put down only enemy tiles up until the boss, gaining the most amount of power possible but with a higher risk of death!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334500/extras/ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1738325456\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Defeat The Ent","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2334500/072fc19070c4e058d3d94a6d0f6ae3522820f2c7.jpg"},{"name":"Defeat The Crystal","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2334500/cf65f904b9e9f41aca0848bf13dda28da998e7ab.jpg"},{"name":"Defeat The Gargoyle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2334500/73bc56d14d4a8e8f1115ea5d656242fa77edc9a3.jpg"},{"name":"Defeat The Mushroom Wizards","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcom